# {{lb|zh|particle placed after monosyllabic verbs}} to [[do]] away with
#: {{zh-x|忘卻|to forget}}
#: {{zh-x|了卻|to end}}
#* {{zh-x|^瑜 駭然 曰：「此 人 有 奪 天地 造化 之 法，鬼神 不測 之 術！若 留 此 人，乃 ^東吳 禍根 也。及 早 殺-卻，免 生 他日 之 憂。」|In consternation {{w|Zhou Yu}} said, "This man has snatched some method from the creative force of Heaven and earth, some unfathomable technic from the world of departed spirits. Why allow him to remain among us and cause trouble, when his elimination would save such great grief?"|ref=''{{w|Romance of the Three Kingdoms}}'' (translation by Yu Sumei)}}
# {{lb|zh|only sentence-medially}} [[but]]; [[yet]]; [[however]]
#: {{zh-x|簡單 卻 有效 的 方法|simple yet effective way}}
#: {{zh-x|我 喜歡 你，卻 不敢 表達。|I love you, '''but''' I do not have the courage to express it.}}
